            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Content Optimization Opportunities</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600">Identify specific elements that drive positive or negative sentiment to optimize future video content and improve audience satisfaction.</p>
